The SP will combine Baidu search services with the popular WeChat social platform (the largest social network in China, with a user base of about 438 million people), Tencent and Wanda infrastructure.
In addition to a network of 40 beautician hotels, the Wanda Group manages at least 49 commercial real estate properties across China and 40 shopping malls.
